            <h3 class="en">Two animated shorts: Taromak Eco-logy and Millet-ology</h3>
            <h3 class="zh">達魯瑪克的家學與小米學</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
            Seed Design | 2020 | 4 Min. | Original with English and Rukai subtitles
        </div>
        <div class="tag-wrap">
            <a href="#" class="tag">#Germanpremiere</a>
